{"tid":431050,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"苟膽講句‼️如果AKB51th單小栗有以唔係Center既話決定退出連登‼️","createTime":"2017-10-10T10:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T12:05:06.000Z","uid":16063,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"87c279ce889cbc9a16525194a2e373d4fbe70ed3","tid":431050,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"100%的ball‼️<br />\n今次有沒人學禾臭禾條女挑戰命運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />‼️<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/94885/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/94885/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/3e8540c19cb08810772357c7e64da651.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F3e8540c19cb08810772357c7e64da651.png&h=dd394e20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83bb3f99baf5cc66ad45396a976d169b779b6032","tid":431050,"uid":51915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:55:01.000Z","msg":"咁你退能硬"},{"pid":"d328b03ffaef8ab98669846c9f36406c1f9e1ed7","tid":431050,"uid":54852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:05:49.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b597f96ed400cd3ad83867e4edb45f742811f9aa","tid":431050,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:16:58.000Z","msg":"小栗有以做51センター三大原因‼️<br />\n<br />\n1)本店握手最快完切成員‼️<br />\n當年美音握手彈起做本店三姐都即刻比左隻44單佢做センター‼️<br />\n而家ゆいゆい直頭係本店一姐‼️<br />\n係呢個成員覺得努力得唔到回報既時期‼️<br />\n好需要比個握手掂既成員做センター黎鎮番努力是有回報的‼️<br />\n<br />\n2)運営同8牙不嬲有仇‼️<br />\n你想出碟⁉️就係唔比你出‼️<br />\n你想獨立⁉️就搵添八成員黎做我地本店センター睇你點獨‼️<br />\n<br />\n3)而家日飯要求本店單獨Single既呼聲越黎越高‼️<br />\n就算最後單獨Singleできません都會搵番個AKB Member黎做C‼️<br />\n至於點解一定係ゆいゆい唔係其他メンバー‼️<br />\n我唔直接答你‼️我用Slumdog Millionaire既結尾一句答你‼️<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/b9610fef701773b91197e850fd34b5b5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2Fb9610fef701773b91197e850fd34b5b5.png&h=05883cf5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ae957